name: 'Love' Archival Giclée Print
description: 'Love' | Limited Edition Giclée Print (photos....) Collage / Mixed Media / Photography Artist : Chris Jones (....) Using a mixture of digital photography, illustration and image manipulation software, Chris’ images often present themselves as altered realities; scenes that are at once familiar, simultaneously obscure, bizarre, puzzling or alien. Chris’ artistic ethos is greatly influenced by the ongoing and often tenuous balance between the dark and light sides of human perception. Of particular interest are the chemical reactions, thoughts and moods that translate, perceive and decode the world outside of us. Giclee prints are printed at the highest resolution (1440 dpi at 8 passes), giving the final image unrivalled quality.

name: Undecided Summer Show 2013 Poster Giclee Print
Undecided #1
description:
'Undecided' is the debut publication from the Undecided Art Collective, a close-knit group of artistic free thinkers mainly based in Ventnor on the Isle of Wight.


Designed with high aesthetics in mind, 'Undecided' builds a platform for which to showcase a myriad of emerging and working artists, photographers and makers locally and internationally.

These Include:

Dixcey, Stuart Harris, Rachael Berry, Stevie Unknown, Julie Barnes, Cendrine Rovini, Julian Winslow, Holly Maslen, Lucie Francis, Leela and the Kat, John Armstrong, Steven Bone, Stephen Butterfield & Chemical Gdns.

* Every copy includes a postcard and badge (whilst stocks last) and we will ship internationally using only robust and environmentally-friendly packaging. * Postage & Packaging costs are nominal, £2 to UK and £5 everywhere else. *One print run only, limited to just 100 copies.
